(.==.) :: Eq b => (a -> b) -> (a -> b) -> a -> Bool
(.<=.) :: Ord b => (a -> b) -> (a -> b) -> a -> Bool
(.&&&.) :: (a -> Bool) -> (a -> Bool) -> a -> Bool
